    "title": "Costa Coffee India Asia Pacific Associates is Hiring: Floor Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Floor Manager with drive and ambition, Costa Coffee India Asia Pacific Associates in Ghaziabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Costa Coffee India Asia Pacific Associates:\nCosta Coffee India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Costa Coffee India Asia Pacific Associates!",
